ActGeneral Campaign Star and General Service Medal Regulations, 2009
SubjectOrder Awarding the General Service Medal With the EXPEDITION Ribbon
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2010-252 of March 10, 2010; (2) determining the eligibility criteria worthy of recognition by the award of the General Service Medal with the EXPEDITION ribbon; (3) specifying the appearance of the EXPEDITION ribbon; and (4) establishing the order of precedence of the General Service Medal with the EXPEDITION ribbon in the Canadian Honours System.
